{"tid":997132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「最親密又可靠」　她竟嫁羽絨被還辦婚禮　","createTime":"2019-01-27T01:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T23:50:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"31d949c24bc828c45dfbed375276d5245c7dacec","tid":997132,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:41:54.000Z","msg":"每到較冷的天氣總會有說離不開溫暖的被窩，但英國有名女子對羽絨被的喜愛已達新境界，高到竟然想到要跟棉被「結婚」，甚至還要替自己舉辦盛大的婚禮，被邀請的貴賓只能穿著睡衣出席，消息一出也立刻引起外界討論。<br />\n《鏡報》報導，英國一名49歲的藝術家薩莉克（Pascale Sellick）形容自己是一個粗魯、愛出風頭的人，所以她要替自己辦一場公開且免費的婚禮，歡迎任何人前來見證，她與人生中相處得最舒服的「伴侶」將共度餘生，而且對象竟然是「羽絨被」，婚禮將在2月10日下午舉行，地點在艾克希特（Exeter）的一處花園。<br />\n薩莉克在與「羽絨被」婚前剖白待嫁的心情，表示「我非常愛我的羽絨被，我想邀請大家來見證我生命中最不變、最令人舒適的伴侶，婚禮當下會有音樂、典禮、笑聲與娛樂活動。」她直指自己與羽絨被之間有著最親密與可靠的關係，「它一直在我身邊，給了我很大的擁抱。」薩莉克坦言還不知道「新郎」會穿什麼服裝，但自己則會穿睡衣與拖鞋。<br />\n薩莉克也希望嘉賓們也穿上無論是睡衣、睡褲、睡袍和連身衣出席，如果天氣太冷，更可以帶自己的睡伴如小熊公仔及暖水壺一同出席。薩莉克補充，自己的婚禮適逢情人節前夕，很高興自己能夠嫁人，「對於很多人來說，情人節可能讓人感到沮喪，希望這有助提升大家的士氣。」她也透露將於婚禮後，到當地的IKEA睡房部享受兩周蜜月假期。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190127/640_5226178284f96d107a08da257f37e5a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190127%2F640_5226178284f96d107a08da257f37e5a9.jpg&h=cf8d6099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190127/640_405521d258663bf251fa52b083ec5b9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190127%2F640_405521d258663bf251fa52b083ec5b9a.jpg&h=68bbac32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190127/640_0c3506321c8f77a208a6d3e3ec7efd35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190127%2F640_0c3506321c8f77a208a6d3e3ec7efd35.jpg&h=5bd224be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190127/640_7bf401be9cf8b59d0112e47a164c6b7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190127%2F640_7bf401be9cf8b59d0112e47a164c6b7f.jpg&h=07cbfa9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190127/640_09f5dae8662d6dc35db30599c9d00753.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190127%2F640_09f5dae8662d6dc35db30599c9d00753.jpg&h=9d14b343&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c2838afbd231c336417d8531a82fbfd6d9fcd89","tid":997132,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"快點"},{"pid":"001e812381d92eac607a4f4c526aeae1dbb8289a","tid":997132,"uid":1067,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"一大堆鴨鵝嘅靈魂喺背後望住你"},{"pid":"6b854e4d4fa73380e2c8db1b04acc2167159e4bc","tid":997132,"uid":55924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T03:44:28.000Z","msg":"夏天係咪踢佢老豆落床<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fc5ed9395dbf538849dc0de3bd074af7198e0d","tid":997132,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b854e4d4fa73380e2c8db1b04acc2167159e4bc","tid":997132,"uid":55924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T03:44:28.000Z","msg":"夏天係咪踢佢老豆落床<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T03:44:39.000Z","msg":"老公"},{"pid":"4513e02743308980ba764a0c0dbd3a18d4389074","tid":997132,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c2838afbd231c336417d8531a82fbfd6d9fcd89","tid":997132,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"快點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T06:51:26.000Z","msg":"咁既樣你都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3b0f345e9bf131c00fd54c15dd32bb543023cd","tid":99